<h1>Edit: <%= crud_label(@book) %></h1>
<p class="text-muted">
  The form is fully derived. <code>slug</code> is read-only
  (<code>editable: false</code>); <code>active</code> is editable only by managers
  (<code>editable: :manage</code> — toggle admin to see it become an input);
  <code>purchase_price</code> is invisible to non-managers entirely
  (<code>if: :manage</code>).
</p>
<div class="card"><div class="card-body">
  <%= crud_form @book %>
</div></div>
